==反響==
===收視及欣賞指數===
[[File:Doctor_Who_(series_1)_viewers.JPG|thumb]]

《羅斯》是整個系列中收看人數最多的一集。在該集播出後的一日，收視報告指英國當晚共有990萬人觀看此集，最高收視達1050萬，[[收視率|收視率]]介於43.2%至44.3%<ref name="ratings">{{cite web | title = Doctor Who is Saturday night hit | publisher = BBC News | date = 2005-03-27 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/4385801.stm | accessdate = 2006-01-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121020031916/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/4385801.stm | archive-date = 2012-10-20 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。最終的報告在結算錄影記錄下，指該集的收看人數是1080萬人，是BBC One當天的收視季軍及全國第七<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.barb.co.uk/viewingsummary/weekreports.cfm?report=weeklyterrestrial&requesttimeout=500 |title=Weekly Viewing Summary: Terrestrial Top 30 - Week ending 6 July 2008 |accessdate=2010-12-30 |publisher=Broadcasters' Audience Research Board |date=2008-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080712091241/http://www.barb.co.uk/viewingsummary/weekreports.cfm?report=weeklyterrestrial&RequestTimeout=500 |archive-date=2008-07-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。至於收看人數最低一集為《玩串真人Show》，數目是681萬人<ref name="viewers">Russell, p. 139</ref>。除了取得高收視外，系列1的劇集還在[[欣賞指數|欣賞指數]]方面得到高分，冠絕所有非[[肥皂劇|肥皂劇]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://blogs.thestage.co.uk/tvtoday/2007/11/these-scifi-people-vote/ |title="These sci-fi people vote" |last=Wright |first=Mark |work=The Stage |date=1-11-2007 |accessdate=30-21-2009 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080409164855/http://blogs.thestage.co.uk/tvtoday/2007/11/these-scifi-people-vote/ |archive-date=2008-04-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。當中，只有《世界末日》一集取得79分，其餘的12集均在80分之上。《背水一戰》更獲得89分，是系列1中得分最高的。在收視和欣賞指數方面的報捷使得BBC決定讓《異世奇人》製作聖誕特輯《[[聖誕入侵|聖誕入侵]]》和系列2<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/4395147.stm |title=New Doctor Who series confirmed |date=2005-03-30 |publisher=BBC News |accessdate=2011-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826113745/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/4395147.stm |archive-date=2014-08-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===專業評價===
2004年4月，{{link-en|米高·格雷德|Michael Grade}}重返BBC擔任理事會主席。格雷德曾在1984年至86年出任BBC One總監一職，後來因不滿舊版《異世奇人》播映而離職年半之多。在2002年的一個訪問中，他更明言對科幻劇沒有好感<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-22628484|title=Was Doctor Who rubbish in the 1980s?|work=Newsround|publisher=BBC|date=2013-05-29|accessdate=2015-02-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141231010017/http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-22628484|archive-date=2014-12-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，當他在2005年6月看畢《異世奇人》系列1後，他在寫給BBC理事長{{link-en|馬克·湯馬臣|Mark Thompson}}的電郵中讚揚此劇，又-{云}-﹕「我從沒想過會寫這電郵的」<ref>{{cite news |first=Jason |last=Dean |title=Doctor Who's greatest enemy finally surrenders |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk_news/story/0,3604,1511605,00.html |work=The Guardian |date=2005-06-22 |accessdate=2011-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070705112054/http://www.guardian.co.uk/uk_news/story/0,3604,1511605,00.html |archive-date=2007-07-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{link-en|第七任博士|Seventh Doctor}}的扮演者[[西爾維斯特·麥考伊|西爾維斯特·麥考伊]]對艾克斯頓和派佩的演出表示讚揚，並對系列1的節奏感到滿意，但他不喜歡[[TARDIS|TARDIS]]的新設計<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/4380477.stm|title=New Who impresses ex-Doctor McCoy|publisher=BBC|date=6-4-2005|accessdate=2011-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110206180133/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/4380477.stm|archive-date=2011-02-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《[[悉尼晨鋒報|悉尼晨鋒報]]》的羅比·奧利華稱戴維斯成功的令《異世奇人》由一部深受成年人喜歡的作品擴展到兒童層面，又指劇集「在科幻市場中有競爭力」<ref name="oliver">{{cite web|first=Robin|last=Oliver|url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/Review/Doctor-Who/2005/05/20/1116533531775.html|title=Doctor Who: Show of the Week|work=The Sydney Morning Herald|date=2005-05-21|accessdate=2012-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921102403/http://www.smh.com.au/news/Review/Doctor-Who/2005/05/20/1116533531775.html|archive-date=2013-09-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外， 奧利華認為老一輩的觀眾會發現艾克斯頓是「繼[[湯姆·貝克|湯姆·貝克]]後最棒的時間領主」<ref name="oliver"/>。對於《羅斯》這集，報章《[[舞台_(報紙)|舞台]]》的哈利·威寧誇讚此作是「非常好、具想想力、有趣又帶點驚嚇的」，又認為泰勒比起舊作的女同伴出色<ref name="harry">{{cite web|first=Harry|last=Venning|url=http://www.thestage.co.uk/features/feature.php/7193/tv-review|title=TV Review|work=The Stage|date=2005-04-04|accessdate=2012-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120819133842/http://www.thestage.co.uk/features/feature.php/7193/tv-review|archive-date=2012-08-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不過，威寧也直言艾克斯頓是劇集「最令人失望之處」，蓋因他看起來令人不舒服<ref name="harry"/>。《Digital Spy》的霍根指《背水一戰》這集是反高潮的，但總的來說整個系列又令人難以遺忘，特別是《戰火孤雛》/《博士之舞》合集<ref name="dek">{{cite web|first=Dek|last=Hogan|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/british-tv/dekstvdiary/a21920/the-global-jukebox.html|title=The Global Jukebox|publisher=Digital Spy|date=2005-06-19|accessdate=2013-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214180709/http://www.digitalspy.com/british-tv/dekstvdiary/a21920/the-global-jukebox.html|archive-date=2013-12-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同時，他又大讚艾克斯頓的演出<ref name="dek"/>。布魯堡在《Now Playing》雜誌給這系列A-的分數，全因其多元化的內容<ref>{{cite web|first=Arnold T |last=Blumburg |url=http://www.nowplayingmag.com/content/view/1844/47/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060623044925/http://www.nowplayingmag.com/content/view/1844/47/ |archivedate=2006-06-23 |title=Doctor Who - Series 1 Wrap-Up |work=Now Playing |date=2006-06-16 |accessdate=2006-06-16 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

網站《DVD Talk》的約翰·辛納特在5星為滿分下給了這系列4星半，寫道﹕「系列具吸引力而又刺激，故成功吸納新觀眾」<ref name="DVD Talk">{{cite web|first=John|last=Sinnott|url=http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/22384/doctor-who-the-complete-first-season/|title=Doctor Who - The Complete First Season|publisher=DVD Talk|date=2006-06-24|accessdate=2013-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120628043523/http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/22384/doctor-who-the-complete-first-season/|archive-date=2012-06-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。與此同時，他又讚揚劇集明節的節奏和包括博士在內的新設計使人耳目一新<ref name="DVD Talk"/>。可是，他覺得戴維斯所寫的劇本「有點瑕疵」，比如泰勒深愛其母{{link-en|積奇·泰勒|Jackie Tyler|積奇}}和男友{{link-en|米基·史密夫|Mickey Smith}}卻又捨下他們，與博士一同探險是不合情理的<ref name="DVD Talk"/>。在2011年，《[[衛報|衛報]]》的史提芬·基利重評系列1，稱劇中的博士雖有不少缺憾，但他依然很棒"<ref name="kelly">{{cite web|first=Stephen|last=Kelly|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/tvandradioblog/2011/jul/21/doctor-who-christopher-eccleston|title=Doctor Who: why did Christopher Eccleston leave show after one series?|work=The Guardian|date=2011-07-21|accessdate=19-12-21011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130718233357/http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/tvandradioblog/2011/jul/21/doctor-who-christopher-eccleston|archive-date=2013-07-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
此外，基利又指全賴艾克斯頓的參與令這劇成為「暫時為止最好、最有名的科幻劇」<ref name="kelly"/>。

儘管《異世奇人》系列1獲得眾多的好評，但不是所有人也滿意此作。比如部份的劇迷就對新設計的標誌和TARDIS表示不滿。為此，他們向劇組成員發{{link-en|恐嚇郵件|hate mail}}以至{{link-en|死亡威脅|Death threat}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.contactmusic.com/new/xmlfeed.nsf/story/dr-who-staff-inundated-with-death-threats |title=Dr Who Staff Inundated With Death Threats |date=2-12-2004 |work=Contactmusic.com |accessdate=2010-12-30 |archive-date=2019-02-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190219175901/http://www.contactmusic.com/doctor-who/news/dr-who-staff-inundated-with-death-threats |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另外，《借屍還魂》一集也遭到一些家長投訴，指這集對小童來說是「過於恐怖」<ref name="scary">{{cite web|first=John|last=Plunkett|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2005/apr/14/bbc.broadcasting|title=Doctor Who 'too scary', say parents|work=The Guardian|date=2005-04-14|accessdate=2011-12-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100406135906/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2005/apr/14/bbc.broadcasting|archive-date=2010-04-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而，BBC不同意此說法，反指《異世奇人》的觀看對象從不包括小童在內<ref name="scary"/>。

===獎項及榮譽===
《異世奇人》系列1在2006年贏得[[英國學術電視獎|英國學術電視獎]]的最佳季度劇集獎及由觀眾投票的先鋒獎（最受歡迎劇集獎）﹔戴維斯則問鼎最佳編劇獎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/4983252.stm|title=Bafta TV Awards 2006: The winners|work=Newsround|publisher=BBC|date=7-5-2006|accessdate=2015-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141125033703/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/4983252.stm|archive-date=2014-11-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，劇集於次一級的{{link-en|威爾斯學術電視獎|BAFTA Cymru}}頒獎禮中一舉奪得5個獎項，當中包括最佳劇集、最佳導演、最佳化妝、最佳服裝以及最佳攝影獎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2006/04_april/24/bafta.shtml|title=BBC Wales' Bafta Cymru success|work=Newsround|publisher=BBC|date=2006-04-24|accessdate=2015-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070708191650/http://www.bbc.co.uk/pressoffice/pressreleases/stories/2006/04_april/24/bafta.shtml|archive-date=2007-07-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，系列1的數集﹕《[[仇人碰面|仇人碰面]]》、《[[父親節_(異世奇人)|父親節]]》及《[[玩串真人Show|玩串真人Show]]》/《[[背水一戰_(異世奇人)|背水一戰]]》合集均入選[[雨果獎|雨果獎]]最佳戲劇呈現（短片）獎。雨果獎的頒獎禮於2006年8月27日在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]舉行，《玩串真人Show》/《背水一戰》合集最終勝出，《仇人碰面》和《父親節》分別排名第二和第三<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.locusmag.com/2006/News/08_HugoCampbellWinners.html |title=Hugo and Campbell Awards Winners |work=Locus Online |accessdate=2006-08-27 |date=2006-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060903090237/http://www.locusmag.com/2006/News/08_HugoCampbellWinners.html |archive-date=2006-09-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同時，系列1獲[[皇家電視學會|皇家電視學會]]提名為最佳季度劇集，但最終不敵BBC Three的醫療劇《{{link-en|軀體 (電視劇)|Bodies (TV series)|軀體}}》<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/4808172.stm |title=Bleak House wins TV drama award |publisher=BBC News |date=2006-12-15 |accessdate=2010-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070216174912/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/4808172.stm |archive-date=2007-02-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。系列1又被英國的{{link-en|廣播記者協會獎|Broadcasting Press Guild}}獲名為最佳劇集，艾克斯頓為最佳男主角、派佩為最佳女主角，但都未能得獎<ref>{{cite web |date=2006-03-31 |url=http://www.broadcastingpressguild.org/awards/2006.html |title=Broadcasting Press Guild Awards 2006 |publisher=Broadcasting Press Guild |accessdate=2010-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722142800/http://www.broadcastingpressguild.org/awards/2006.html |archive-date=2011-07-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不過，派佩在隨後舉行的{{link-en|南岸節日獎|Broadcasting Press Guild}}憑泰勒一角獲得冒起英國演員突破獎<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/doctorwho/news/cult/news/drwho/2006/01/30/29231.shtml |title=More awards |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060208083501/http://www.bbc.co.uk/doctorwho/news/cult/news/drwho/2006/01/30/29231.shtml |archivedate=2006-02-08 |publisher=BBC |date=2006-01-30 |accessdate=2012-03-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

劇集還得到公眾的喜愛。在2005年，《異世奇人》系列1取得[[國家電視獎|國家電視獎]]的最受歡迎劇集獎，艾克斯頓和派佩分別得最受歡迎男主角和女主角獎<ref>{{cite news |title=Dr Who scores TV awards hat-trick |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6104048.stm |publisher=BBC News |date=2006-10-31 |accessdate=2006-10-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070106045321/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6104048.stm |archive-date=2007-01-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《博士之舞》問鼎BBC頒發的黃金電視時刻金獎<ref>{{cite web |date=12-2005 |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/tvmoments/winners.shtml |title=2005 TV Moments |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2010-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111014073443/http://www.bbc.co.uk/tvmoments/winners.shtml |archive-date=2011-10-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同時，網民通過BBC.co.uk票選出《異世奇人》為最佳劇集，艾克斯頓以59.42%當選為最佳男主角，派佩以59.76%的得票率成為最佳女主角<ref>{{cite web |date=12-2005 |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/drama/bestof2005/best_actor.shtml |title=Drama – Best of 2005 – Best Actor |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2010-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090420132245/http://www.bbc.co.uk/drama/bestof2005/best_actor.shtml |archive-date=2009-04-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |date=12-2005 |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/drama/bestof2005/best_actress.shtml |title=Drama – Best of 2005 – Best Actress |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2010-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101109215331/http://www.bbc.co.uk/drama/bestof2005/best_actress.shtml |archive-date=2010-11-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，她還取得最合意明星獎，得票率是26.47%<ref>{{cite web|date=12-2005|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/drama/bestof2005/most_desirable_star.shtml|title=Drama – Best of 2005 – Most Desirable Star|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2010-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090420121734/http://www.bbc.co.uk/drama/bestof2005/most_desirable_star.shtml|archive-date=2009-04-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>﹔《異世奇人》的官方網頁以71.17%高票贏得最佳網頁獎<ref>{{cite web |date=12-2005 |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/drama/bestof2005/best_site.shtml |title=Drama – Best of 2005 – Best Drama Website |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2010-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090420084510/http://www.bbc.co.uk/drama/bestof2005/best_site.shtml |archive-date=2009-04-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。-{[[戴立克|戴立克]]}-在《仇人碰面》一集回歸成為網民心目中的最愛時刻，這外星生物又以46.40%加冕最佳逆角獎<ref>{{cite web |date=12-2005 |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/drama/bestof2005/best_villain.shtml |title=Drama – Best of 2005 – Best Villain |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2010-12-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090420141115/http://www.bbc.co.uk/drama/bestof2005/best_villain.shtml |archive-date=2009-04-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

